# Styling & Component Patterns

## UI Framework
- Tailwind CSS 4.x with shadcn/ui components
- Use [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui/) for reusable components
- Follow shadcn/ui patterns for component structure

## Button Component Pattern
From [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx):
- Use `class-variance-authority` for variant management
- Support `asChild` prop with Radix Slot
- Include proper TypeScript variant props
- Use `cn()` utility for class merging

## Styling Guidelines
- Use semantic color tokens (primary, secondary, destructive, etc.)
- Include focus-visible and accessibility states
- Support dark mode variants
- Use Tailwind arbitrary values sparingly

## Icon Usage
- Lucide React for consistent iconography
- Size icons appropriately: `size-4` for buttons, etc.
- Use semantic icon names (Plus, Trash2, Edit2, etc.)

## Layout Patterns
- Use flexbox for component layouts
- Implement proper spacing with Tailwind spacing scale
- Follow mobile-first responsive design principles